unittitle_ssm: Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Printed Ephemera Collection on the Socialist Party (U.S.)
abstract_ssm: The collection consists of leaflets, flyers, manifestoes, reports, memoranda, executive committee minutes, pamphlets, a ledger and other internal documents generated by the Socialist Party of America.  Also included are related organizations such as Socialist Democratic Federation, Young People's Socialist League and Socialist Party USA. The collection offers a general feel for the types of printed matter put out by the Party as well as a brief introduction to and history of the Party and how it changed over the years.
